  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "There are number of design patterns to achieve Parallelization with Multicore system. We will see some of those in this page"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Master/Worker design pattern"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Master core (Master) executes the code until it reaches an area when it can be parallelized. Then triggers the workers in another cores (Core 1 and Core 2) to perform the computationally intensive work."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Once the worker finishes work, Master starts again and completes the work"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "/confluence/download/attachments/2476796598/Master_Worker.png?version=1&modificationDate=1666762191000&api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore Design Patterns/Master_Worker.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Peer design pattern"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This is same as Master/worker but here Master also shares the computationally intensive work with other cores"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "/confluence/download/attachments/2476796598/Copy%20of%20Master_Worker.png?version=3&modificationDate=1666762609000&api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore Design Patterns/Copy of Master_Worker.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Pipelined design pattern"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In this pattern, application is divided into 'series of smaller, independent stages' - Where output of stage is input to the next"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Each stage can be placed in different core"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "/confluence/download/attachments/2476796598/Pipelined.png?version=1&modificationDate=1666764223000&api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore Design Patterns/Pipelined.png"
    }
  ],
